<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:19:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>早盘竞价：苹果焦虑、特斯拉坦克、比特币犹豫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>法国“蜘蛛侠”攀登塔楼支持菲律宾南海主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，一名被称为“法国蜘蛛侠”的自由攀登者爬上了马尼拉的一座摩天大楼，以支持菲律宾在有争议的南中国海的海洋主张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙建筑商 Mota-Engil 2023 年利润增长一倍多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/portuguese-builder-mota-engil-more-than-doubles-2023-profit-2024-03-05/</link><description>葡萄牙最大的建筑商周二表示，Mota-Engil 的 2023 年净利润增长了一倍多，销售额创历史新高，而需求将其订单量推升至前所未有的 130 亿欧元（141 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/portuguese-builder-mota-engil-more-than-doubles-2023-profit-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：碧桂园贷款人集团聘请顾问进行债务重组谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</link><description>三位知情人士称，中国碧桂园的一组贷款人已聘请安理国际会计师事务所(Allen &amp;amp; Overy)和德勤(Deloitte)作为顾问，而这家陷入困境的开发商的债权人正在为可能的债务重组谈判做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾敦促与中国进行无政治先决条件的对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</link><description>北京在一份政府工作报告中强化了在台湾问题上的立场后，台湾陆委会周二敦促中国接受两岸互不隶属的事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济刺激措施乏善可陈，欧洲股市下跌，经济数据成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</link><description>欧洲股市周二走低，原因是中国在增长乏力的情况下转型经济的承诺未能给投资者留下深刻印象，而市场在一系列欧元区和美国经济数据公布之前变得谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:16:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车 2 月份销量下滑 2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-february-sales-volume-down-2-year-on-year-2024-03-05/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的沃尔沃汽车公司周二表示，2月份销量同比下降2%至50,315辆，并指出中国农历新年是销量下降的主要原因。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-february-sales-volume-down-2-year-on-year-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>德国舍弗勒2023年核心利润未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</link><description>德国汽车和工业供应商舍弗勒股份公司周二公布的 2023 年全年调整后核心利润 (EBIT) 为 11.9 亿（12.9 亿美元），受到中国对该集团工业部门需求疲软的拖累。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国将在面向南海和台湾的岛屿举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</link><description>随着该地区与中国的紧张局势持续发酵，菲律宾和美国将于下个月在菲律宾面临南海的岛屿和台湾等关键地点举行年度军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国迅速崛起的军事实力“令人严重担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-chinas-rapidly-rising-military-power-serious-concern-2024-03-05/</link><description>日本内阁官房长官林芳正周二表示，中国迅速扩张的军事实力令日本和国际社会“严重关切”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:26:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-chinas-rapidly-rising-military-power-serious-concern-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于财政火箭弹难以捉摸，中国投资者坚持逢低买入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</link><description>重返正在复苏的中国股市的外国投资者表示，周二宣布的支出计划不足以扭转低迷的情绪，目前继续购买股票的主要原因是它们价格便宜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军称约翰·芬恩号航空母舰进行了从南到北台湾海峡的例行过境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-says-uss-john-finn-conducted-routine-south-to-north-taiwan-strait-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国海军周二在一份声明中表示，阿利-伯克级导弹驱逐舰约翰·芬恩号于3月5日进行了例行的南北台湾海峡过境。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-says-uss-john-finn-conducted-routine-south-to-north-taiwan-strait-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国的目标是科技自力更生；誓言向外国投资者开放制造业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-aims-self-reliance-tech-vows-open-manufacturing-foreign-investors-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国周二誓言要建立从人工智能到太空等对未来竞争力至关重要的产业，同时开放制造业和一些服务业的准入，以阻止外国投资者撤退。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-aims-self-reliance-tech-vows-open-manufacturing-foreign-investors-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商恢复英国商业地产撤退</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</link><description>房地产经纪人表示，一些大型中国开发商将出售更多英国房地产以筹集现金，充分利用缓慢解冻的市场和押注复苏的买家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>Cryptoverse：亚洲交易员掀起比特币热潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cryptoverse-asian-traders-give-bitcoin-blast-off-2024-03-05/</link><description>比特币的疯狂上涨是由亚洲投资者推动的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cryptoverse-asian-traders-give-bitcoin-blast-off-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>